OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after doing viral
OL,4,C'Chroming' challenge
OL,6,FRajiv Popat has been speaking to
OL,7,FTiegan Jarman's family.
OL,9,FThe family of a 13-year-old girl from
OL,10,FLeicestershire say she died after
OL,11,Ftaking part in a deadly social media
OL,12,Ftrend.
OL,14,FTiegan Jarman, who lived in
OL,15,FThurmaston, was found unresponsive in
OL,16,Fher bedroom on Thursday, March 6, this
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FEmergency services attempted to
OL,20,Fresuscitate her, but she died at the
OL,21,Fscene.
