OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after doing viral
OL,4,C'Chroming' challenge
OL,6,FHer parents say she'd been taking part
OL,7,Fin the 'Chroming' challenge after
OL,8,Fcopying videos from TikTok.
OL,10,FHer mum, Sonia Hopkin, said she didn't
OL,11,Fbelieve it when her husband called
OL,12,Fher: "Her dad called me and said she
OL,13,Fhad passed away, and I said 'No, she's
OL,14,Fnot, you're lying.' And he said, 'No,
OL,15,Fshe's passed away.'
OL,17,F"I didn't know anything, I didn't know
OL,18,Fany answers, I just knew my daughter
OL,19,Fisn't alive. She was only 13. She's
OL,20,Fnot poorly; she was fit and healthy. I
OL,21,Fonly saw her the day before."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
