OL,6,FMrs Hopkin described the moment the
OL,7,Fpolice found her daughter: "The police
OL,8,Fwere called as well, and they found a
OL,9,Fdeodorant right next to my daughter,
OL,10,FTiegan.
OL,12,F"And there was one close by as well,
OL,13,Fso there were actually two deodorant
OL,14,Fcans in the room."
