OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after doing viral
OL,4,C'Chroming' challenge
OL,6,FTiegan's sister, Alisha Wade, said she
OL,7,Flooked through her sister's social
OL,8,Fmedia after her death, "I saw her
OL,9,Freposts, and I saw her reposting about
OL,10,Fthis challenge. Why are people making
OL,11,Fthese videos? It's not fun. It's
OL,12,Fserious, and they were taking it so
OL,13,Funseriously."
OL,15,FWhat is Chroming?
OL,17,FChroming involves inhaling toxic fumes
OL,18,Ffrom common household items, which can
OL,19,Fcause brain damage and heart attacks.
