OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after doing viral
OL,4,C'Chroming' challenge
OL,6,FThe name came from the silver colour
OL,7,Fleft behind after inhaling chrome-
OL,8,Fbased spray paint.
OL,10,FVideos encouraging the trend went
OL,11,Fviral in Australia back in 2023, with
OL,12,Fmany gaining millions of views. Since
OL,13,Fthen, the deaths of several children
OL,14,Fhave been linked to it.
OL,16,FTiegan had three siblings, Brogan, 24,
OL,17,FCallum, 17, and a sister, Alisha, 18,
OL,18,Falongside four step-siblings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
