OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after doing viral
OL,4,C'Chroming' challenge
OL,6,FAlisha has now started an online
OL,7,Fpetition in a bid to make the dangers
OL,8,Fof social media trends a mandatory
OL,9,Fprogram in schools.
OL,11,F"I didn't know about it until my
OL,12,Fsister died. I've messaged my friends
OL,13,Fabout it and they didn't know about it
OL,14,Fand we're all 18 so younger kids are
OL,15,Fgoing to keep doing it and there are
OL,16,Fgoing to be more lives lost."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
