OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after doing viral
OL,4,C'Chroming' challenge
OL,6,FShe is also calling for changes to
OL,7,Faerosol sales, "The labelling on the
OL,8,Fcans. It's too small. I can't read it
OL,9,Fsometimes. We want the items to be 16+
OL,10,For even 18+. So young kids like my
OL,11,Fsister can stop buying these."
OL,13,FMrs Hopkin supports the petition and
OL,14,Fsays she is shocked by what she sees
OL,15,Fon social media, "I go on social media
OL,16,Fto monitor the sites and be aware of
OL,17,Fwhat's being posted, reposted...from
OL,18,Fkids who are actually participating in
OL,19,Fthese challenges.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
