OL,6,F"Just take them down. Take them down.
OL,7,FI also want it to be in schools so
OL,8,Fchildren are taught about it alongside
OL,9,Fsex education."
OL,11,FThe petition, titled 'Enforce warnings
OL,12,Fon solvent products and educate on
OL,13,Frisks' also hopes to see more
OL,14,Fprominent warning labels on
OL,15,Fpotentially dangerous products.
OL,17,FThe British Aerosol Manufacturers'
OL,18,FAssociation says aerosol products
OL,19,Falready have warnings, but they're
OL,20,Fchanging the wording to make it
OL,21,Fsimpler in 2026.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
