OL,3,CGirl, 13, dies after doing viral
OL,4,C'Chroming' challenge
OL,6,FA spokesperson for TikTok told us this
OL,7,Fincident deeply saddens the company.
OL,9,FIn a statement, they said, "Content
OL,10,Fpromoting dangerous challenges is not
OL,11,Fallowed on TikTok, and we proactively
OL,12,Fremoved 99.8% of videos that violated
OL,13,Four policies on this issue before they
OL,14,Fwere reported to us.
OL,16,F"Searches for this particular
OL,17,Fchallenge are blocked and we have
OL,18,Ffound no evidence of it ever having
OL,19,Fbeen a trend on our platform."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
